sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Faculty
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as Backend
  participant ML as ML Service
  participant XAI as Explainability
  participant DB as Database

  U->>FE: Click "Run prediction" on student
  FE->>API: POST /api/v1/predictions/{student_id}
  API->>DB: Load student
  API->>ML: build_features(student)
  ML->>ML: Lazy-load model.joblib (first time only)
  ML-->>API: probabilities + argmax class
  API->>XAI: explain(model, features, sample)
  alt SHAP available
    XAI-->>API: signed feature contributions
  else SHAP missing
    XAI-->>API: permutation-based contributions
  end
  API->>API: Compose narrative sentence
  API->>DB: INSERT predictions, risk_history
  API->>DB: INSERT audit_logs(action='prediction.create')
  API-->>FE: 200 { risk_level, confidence, top_factors, narrative }
  FE->>U: Render RiskMeter + ExplainabilityPanel
